{"tid":1732041,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"11月18日，陣地戰將我哋所有精銳一網打盡","createTime":"2019-11-17T22:23:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T07:31:19.000Z","uid":185416,"like":12,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"782a3d77c33e09652e8bffe16439933b0e026980","tid":1732041,"uid":185416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T22:23:06.000Z","msg":"又好耐以前已經開始話要Be water<br />\n到今日所有精銳俾人一網打盡<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解由中大開始，大家忽然迷戀左陣地戰<br />\n聽聞今日四支最強勁嘅勇武小隊，同埋老竇搵仔將會收皮<br />\n<br />\n我已經知道我哋已經輸咗<br />\n對唔住，我知道冇人想接受呢個現實<br />\n<br />\n但係11月18號，的確係有史以來損失最慘重嘅一日<br />\n救唔到人不特止，出嚟救人嘅都死傷慘重<br />\n<br />\n相信曱甴嘅行為將會更加變本加厲，因為佢哋今日所做嘅事唔會有後果，即使佢哋話要重演六四，即使佢哋話要劏曱甴，即使佢哋將所有護士/醫生用索帶綁住<br />\n<br />\n跟咗人性本惡嘅定理，相信只會有更多嘅女士俾人強姦，同埋更多嘅男士俾人雞姦，同埋更多人死更多人受傷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我亦都相信，香港人今日會照常返工<br />\n因為，因為會出嚟嘅人尋日已經出晒黎<br />\n唔會出嚟嘅人，即使到天光...<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">佢哋都係唔會出嚟</span>"},{"pid":"9a613504839c67ba8b2e12b72f9e50aa0465f477","tid":1732041,"uid":46151,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T22:24:22.000Z","msg":"開呢個垃圾post有撚用"},{"pid":"8f52ad3553a89f9f5407208c95753496b8292489","tid":1732041,"uid":50284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T22:27:28.000Z","msg":"今日係要大家一齊<span style=\"color: red;\">向前衝</span>！！！<br />\n唔會有路入到去理大，因為全部封晒，今日出得黎就預左要大家一齊衝防線<br />\n<br />\n我知，我知係需要好大既勇氣...<br />\n<br />\n但理大既手足、香港既未來就係需要<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你依份勇氣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n口號：<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">衝呀！手足！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">車撞狗，屠狗都唔割呀！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n漆咸道北集結反攻入去打出破口"},{"pid":"498103e95adfb7c23a11eb58b7b38b66e25a2b06","tid":1732041,"uid":67292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T22:29:07.000Z","msg":"要屌都唔係呢個時候，救人啊！"},{"pid":"24ac1f4be45199813708b9ef5ae9c77c00d16e8b","tid":1732041,"uid":216603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T22:29:08.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"fdadfc45bb635522fefbd696014ed5cec4388e65","tid":1732041,"uid":185416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"498103e95adfb7c23a11eb58b7b38b66e25a2b06","tid":1732041,"uid":67292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T22:29:07.000Z","msg":"要屌都唔係呢個時候，救人啊！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T22:29:59.000Z","msg":"救左一晚啊<br />\n在頂落去真係會死<br />\n對唔住，要撤退"},{"pid":"c41c3eea0fd747796f94267d9fcd9d1b3cde7e98","tid":1732041,"uid":151378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T22:31:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fef4d1d587953bee7529b3a9787e6feb1e4dcea0","tid":1732041,"uid":185416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c41c3eea0fd747796f94267d9fcd9d1b3cde7e98","tid":1732041,"uid":151378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T22:31:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T22:32:42.000Z","msg":"冇辦法，食返10粒安眠藥先訓<br />\n希望醒咗第二個世界"},{"pid":"0d76bcd559cbc21db96264ed48f687aebcde845d","tid":1732041,"uid":284804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T22:35:02.000Z","msg":"軍事要地 講完 唔撚守我睇你罷乜撚嘢"},{"pid":"2712a4bdf767f8f82cdf0c18941254b9eca5ff69","tid":1732041,"uid":151378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T22:36:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6bdf71f9d8ebfe7508c3f0d935ef76419c8f9eaa","tid":1732041,"uid":284804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2712a4bdf767f8f82cdf0c18941254b9eca5ff69","tid":1732041,"uid":151378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d76bcd559cbc21db96264ed48f687aebcde845d","tid":1732041,"uid":284804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T22:35:02.000Z","msg":"軍事要地 講完 唔撚守我睇你罷乜撚嘢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T22:36:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"r